{"tid":1251603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港天主教大專聯會向教宗遞信  介紹近日示威","createTime":"2019-06-22T15:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T15:03:29.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6372a49c9a4b5f889709664cf095ec9b860e1faa","tid":1251603,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:03:29.000Z","msg":"香港天主教大專聯會 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/65585090_2186456214801757_3328318922452631552_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQkBTTZPQxpZ5qcpo3p3wCKWTfhSAlcg9kNDvAaSYXGdgGUFd5mmyKhb59OGKl0_oJI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=89b919d8d72adf3b83f470c3b5df12ba&amp;oe=5D7B9A3C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F65585090_2186456214801757_3328318922452631552_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQkBTTZPQxpZ5qcpo3p3wCKWTfhSAlcg9kNDvAaSYXGdgGUFd5mmyKhb59OGKl0_oJI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D89b919d8d72adf3b83f470c3b5df12ba%26oe%3D5D7B9A3C&h=87f0475b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前，本會兩位成員，中大天主教同學會會長吳穎堯（見圖）、明愛專上學院天主教同學會會長黃軍龍代表香港教區前往羅馬，出席國際青年論壇。<br />\n<br />\n兩位同學於今（22）日獲教宗接見，並向教宗呈上信函，介紹香港近日反對逃犯條例修訂的示威，以及公教青年在是次運動中的角色。藉此機會，他們亦請教宗繼續關心和顧念香港社會。"}]}